  <brief_title>A Rehabilitation Program for Adolescents With Chronic Fatigue Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Integrative Approach Based Psychoeducation, Heart Rate Variability Coherence Biofeedback and Elements of, Pacing Cognitive Behavior Therapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
